features: MOUTHWASH: Listerine antiseptic mouthwash kills 99.9% of germs that cause bad breath, plaque, and gingivitis; Leaves your mouth feeling fresh and clean when used as part of your regular oral hygiene routine; Cool Mint flavor.

ANTISEPTIC: Mouthwash that supports healthy gums & is clinically shown to reduce 52% more plaque and reduce gingivitis by 21% more than brushing and flossing alone; Destroys 5x more plaque above the gumline than floss*; Fresh breath & germ* protection.

BAD BREATH TREATMENT: Listerine mouthwash is infused with a cool mint flavor that leaves your mouth feeling clean and freshens breath after only one use; Deep clean effects from the refreshing minty flavor; Mouthwash to help fight Gum Disease.

#1 DENTIST RECOMMENDED: ADA-Approved and from the #1 Dentist recommended brand for over the counter mouthwashes; Listerine mouthwash has been clinically studied for over 75 years and is the most widely used mouthwash in the world.

INCLUDES: Pack of 2, 1 L mouthwash; Use regularly during your oral care routine to help contribute to overall good oral hygiene; Rinse for 30 seconds both morning and night or otherwise instructed by a dentist or physician.
body.description: Protect your mouth from germs and get fresh breath with the Listerine Cool Mint Antiseptic Mouthwash. Accepted by the American Dental Association (ADA), this germ-killing mouthwash for bad breath is clinically shown to reduce plaque 52 percent more and reduce gingivitis 21 percent more than brushing and flossing alone. Adding a 30-second rinse of this refreshing mint flavored oral rinse to your morning and evening oral hygiene routines is all it takes to get 24-hour germ protection against those that cause bad breath, plaque, and gingivitis. From the #1 dentist recommended brand** of over the counter mouthwashes, Listerine Cool Mint Antiseptic Mouthwash contains the antiplaque and antigingivitis ingredients eucalyptol, menthol, methyl salicylate and thymol. *Germ kill provides sustained plaque reduction after a dental cleaning. Rinse is not intended to replace brushing or flossing. Use product only as directed. *when used twice daily **IQVIA survey May 2022-2023

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I highly recommend
reviews.reviewText: I first came across Listerine Cool Mint during a visit to the dentist last year. It caught my eye, and I even snapped a picture of it. Since then, I haven't stopped using it, and let me tell you, it's transformed my oral hygiene routine. The cool mint flavor is incredibly refreshing, leaving my mouth feeling clean and rejuvenated every time. Not only does it provide long-lasting fresh breath, but I also appreciate its effectiveness in killing germs that cause bad breath and plaque buildup.Without a doubt, I highly recommend Listerine Cool Mint to anyone seeking a dependable mouthwash that truly delivers results.
